when I first downloaded I thought it was great. Had good info & looked nice. 

Then, I started to notice my skin starting to have this faint peachy tint and my hair was turned this piss yellow color. I didn’t think it had any connection with the app

Then, a few weeks later, I noticed that I had gradually gained 50 lbs!! WTH!!! 

The app would make random screeching and whining noises if I weren’t giving it attention

so I went to my doctors and they asked me if I had any change in routine. 
I mean not really, we’re all in quarantine!! 

So then that got me thinking. I recently downloaded this app!! So I deleted the app and won’t be downloading it again 🤢🤢
